/Berkpic7.jpg?pfqQzc8AMDO9Bu9B WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> a life</span><hr size=1> i wish i could just go to a place, real or not, that i could get away from all this stupid @#%$ that's happening.  My mom is going crazy because of bills, and my dad's death, and everthing else, so she feels she has to drink to get through it all.  My girlfriend...i know she feels bad for me, but i also know she doesn't understand it.  Still she pulls me through everyday, and i love her.  My dad, he died about 2 years ago.  I never really knew how much i needed him until he was gone.  Never take anyone for granted that you love, you'll regret it a lot.  I know i do.  It feels like i am having to hold up my family, and i'm just 18.  I wish i was 12 again, no worries at all.  Mow I have to worry about school, my girlfriend, my mom, my friends, my band, how i'm going to survive on my own....it's just so much, that i don't need.  I just need somewhere to go, somewhere that i can breathe in deep, and know that I don't have to worry about anything.  Not taking care of my drunk mom, not worrying about if my dad is proud of me now, or if he ever was.  I don't want to have to worry about anything.  I love it when i can just lie in Molly's arms, and let her kiss away all the bad stuff.  That's when i'm really happy..when she's happy.  I guess i'll get a little rest sometime before i die.  haha, not likely though if everything keeps going the way it has been for the past couple of years.  I need a rest. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/upuerumbris.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Puer Umbris </A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(2/25/02 3:13:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=522.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img sr